    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Format CAC alert WhatsApp message for founder\nconst kpi = $input.first().json;\n\nconst msg = `🚨 *KoneksAI KPI ALERT*\n\n⚠️ CAC depase $20 jodi a!\n\n📊 *Chif jodi a (${kpi.date}):*\n• CAC: $${kpi.cac_usd} USD ⬆️ TWÒP\n• Nouvo kliyan: ${kpi.new_clients}\n• Depans Meta Ads: $${kpi.total_ad_spend_usd}\n• Nouvo leads: ${kpi.new_leads}\n• Konvèsyon: ${(kpi.conversion_rate * 100).toFixed(1)}%\n\n🎯 *Aksyon rekòmande:*\n1. Tcheke pèfòmans kanpay Meta la\n2. Rann tèt ou sèten kreyatif an travay\n3. Konsidere redui bidji jouk konvèsyon monte\n\nLTV aktyèl: $${kpi.ltv_usd}/ane`;\n\nreturn [{ json: { ...kpi, alert_message: msg } }];"
      },
      "id": "node-format-cac-alert",
      "name": "Format CAC Alert",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1520, 280]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "=https://graph.facebook.com/v19.0/{{ $env.WHATSAPP_PHONE_NUMBER_ID }}/messages",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpHeaderAuth",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"messaging_product\": \"whatsapp\",\n  \"recipient_type\": \"individual\",\n  \"to\": \"{{ $env.FOUNDER_WHATSAPP }}\",\n  \"type\": \"text\",\n  \"text\": {\n    \"preview_url\": false,\n    \"body\": {{ JSON.stringify($json.alert_message) }}\n  }\n}",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 10000
        }
      },
      "id": "node-wa-cac-alert",
      "name": "WhatsApp: CAC Alert to Founder",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4,
      "position": [1760, 280],
      "credentials": {
        "httpHeaderAuth": {
          "id": "wa-header-auth-001",
          "name": "WhatsApp Bearer Token"
